1
00:00:12,371 --> 00:00:15,811
♪Have you ever heard about that♪

2
00:00:15,811 --> 00:00:18,691
♪the cliff of a snow mountain♪

3
00:00:19,211 --> 00:00:24,331
♪once fascinated numerous people?♪

4
00:00:26,011 --> 00:00:29,251
♪Legend has it that,♪

5
00:00:29,251 --> 00:00:32,051
♪there were treasures at the peak♪

6
00:00:32,891 --> 00:00:37,971
♪but also there was a bottomless chasm hidden over there.♪

7
00:00:39,571 --> 00:00:43,011
♪The smart, the fool♪

8
00:00:43,051 --> 00:00:45,851
♪and the kind people,♪

9
00:00:46,491 --> 00:00:52,331
♪all are familiar to you.♪

10
00:00:53,211 --> 00:00:56,771
♪On the mountainside, on the cliff,♪

11
00:00:57,091 --> 00:00:59,691
♪on the cloud,♪

12
00:01:00,091 --> 00:01:05,211
♪and in the human world,♪

13
00:01:17,051 --> 00:01:24,331
♪snowflakes are drifting profusely and disorderly.♪

14
00:01:36,091 --> 00:01:40,091
=Joy of Life Special Edition=

15
00:01:40,091 --> 00:01:43,011
=Episode 7=

16
00:01:55,879 --> 00:01:57,200
What did he say to you?

17
00:01:58,480 --> 00:01:59,319
He's already dead

18
00:02:00,439 --> 00:02:01,519
when I'm here.

19
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:11,560
You said

20
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:14,439
you'd only die for your family.

21
00:02:16,759 --> 00:02:17,960
You said you'd run away

22
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:19,319
in case of danger.

23
00:02:20,319 --> 00:02:22,159
Why did you break your words?

24
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:39,599
He's not dead.

25
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:41,000
Your Excellency.

26
00:02:43,319 --> 00:02:43,840
Your Excellency.

27
00:02:43,919 --> 00:02:44,439
Go away.

28
00:02:44,599 --> 00:02:45,159
Get out of the way!

29
00:02:45,159 --> 00:02:45,759
Your Excellency.

30
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:46,879
He is alive!

31
00:02:47,199 --> 00:02:48,639
and avenge Teng Zijing's death

32
00:02:48,639 --> 00:02:50,240
if he dies.

33
00:02:56,879 --> 00:02:57,879
Who will interrogate him?

34
00:02:59,159 --> 00:03:00,000
I also don't know

35
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:12,080
Take Teng Zijing to the Fan mansion.

36
00:03:12,759 --> 00:03:13,439
Got it.

37
00:03:14,199 --> 00:03:15,080
I will

38
00:03:16,039 --> 00:03:17,840
go to the Investigator's Office
for the result tomorrow.

39
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:22,919
Your Excellency,
let me go back with you.

40
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:23,719
No.

41
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:27,560
No matter who it is,

42
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:31,000
I'll give them one more chance
to kill me.

43
00:03:48,199 --> 00:03:49,240
Why is he so seriously injured?

44
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:50,639
Yeah. Where is he going?

45
00:03:57,159 --> 00:03:58,439
Brother, what's up?

46
00:03:59,919 --> 00:04:00,639
I'm good.

47
00:04:01,599 --> 00:04:02,520
I've heard.

48
00:04:02,680 --> 00:04:03,479
It's all in the past.

49
00:04:05,639 --> 00:04:07,599
Send someone to tell Li Chengze

50
00:04:08,599 --> 00:04:09,800
an accident has happened to me

51
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:11,879
and I can't make it today.

52
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:15,039
Ruoruo,

53
00:04:16,879 --> 00:04:18,160
we're not going back to Danzhou.

54
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:37,240
I'm afraid it's bad news.

55
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:42,680
Cheng Jushu tried
to assassinate Fan Xian

56
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:43,399
on Niulan Street.

57
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:45,160
And then?

58
00:04:45,680 --> 00:04:46,759
Two female assassins

59
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:48,120
and Fan Xian's guard were killed.

60
00:04:48,879 --> 00:04:49,800
Is Cheng Jushu still alive?

61
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:52,000
He's taken away
by the Investigator's Office.

62
00:04:52,519 --> 00:04:53,879
They must want
to find the one behind this.

63
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:56,279
Here is the capital city.

64
00:04:56,759 --> 00:04:57,800
Who dared to do that here?

65
00:04:59,079 --> 00:05:00,759
I'll be considered
the most likely suspect.

66
00:05:01,399 --> 00:05:01,920
Your Highness.

67
00:05:03,079 --> 00:05:04,439
It's me that asked Fan Xian to be here

68
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:06,399
and he was attacked on his way.

69
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:08,000
Your Highness, let's go back.

70
00:05:27,079 --> 00:05:28,120
This matter

71
00:05:30,759 --> 00:05:32,759
may shock the whole city.

72
00:05:37,680 --> 00:05:39,160
Luckily, Fan Xian is all right.

73
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:49,759
But, you're not shocked at all.

74
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:01,399
Your Highness, what do you mean?

75
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:03,920
I don't understand.

76
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:16,759
You're not surprised

77
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:18,680
when hearing about
the assassination attempt.

78
00:06:20,439 --> 00:06:22,120
Did you expect

79
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:23,519
it would happen?

80
00:06:28,839 --> 00:06:30,040
What are you going to do?

81
00:06:32,639 --> 00:06:35,319
I didn't mean it.
Don't take it seriously.

82
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:22,879
Cheng Jushu is in custody
at the Investigator's Office.

83
00:07:28,879 --> 00:07:29,639
Ruoruo

84
00:07:29,639 --> 00:07:31,240
has been waiting at the gate

85
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:33,240
for the result.

86
00:07:37,079 --> 00:07:39,279
Who do you think it might be?

87
00:07:49,079 --> 00:07:51,399
Li Chengze is the most likely suspect.

88
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:53,000
It's he that

89
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:55,279
asked you to go to Joy Tsin House

90
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:58,759
and you have to pass through
Niulan Street to get there.

91
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:03,279
If I were dead,

92
00:08:04,439 --> 00:08:05,399
everyone would suspect him.

93
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:09,120
So, it's someone else.

94
00:08:15,199 --> 00:08:16,399
I want to know

95
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:19,920
where the Crown Prince went

96
00:08:20,279 --> 00:08:20,920
and what he did today.

97
00:08:21,279 --> 00:08:22,600
You don't have the right

98
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:24,480
to ask about his whereabouts.

99
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:30,319
The one behind the scenes
is still a mystery.

100
00:08:30,519 --> 00:08:33,320
Don't act rashly.

101
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:41,879
I'm done.

102
00:09:41,519 --> 00:09:42,399
I've heard.

103
00:09:45,559 --> 00:09:46,919
I've heard it's a fierce battle.

104
00:09:48,759 --> 00:09:49,960
I've been worried about you.

105
00:09:51,039 --> 00:09:51,840
Teng Zijing.

106
00:09:54,519 --> 00:09:55,320
Is he dead?

107
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:01,600
He was your guard.

108
00:10:04,919 --> 00:10:05,879
No, he wasn't.

109
00:10:10,399 --> 00:10:11,519
He was an idiot.

110
00:10:30,039 --> 00:10:31,759
Who tried to assassinate Fan Xian?

111
00:10:33,519 --> 00:10:34,679
I'm ignorant sometimes,

112
00:10:34,919 --> 00:10:36,399
but I'd never dare to do that.

113
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:38,279
I've been getting well along
with Fan Xian.

114
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:40,360
I really have no reason to kill him.

115
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:42,279
Then who do you think it is?

116
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:44,799
The assassinators are warriors
from Beiqi.

117
00:10:45,200 --> 00:10:46,879
It may be their plot.

118
00:10:47,919 --> 00:10:49,120
It makes sense.

119
00:10:49,120 --> 00:10:51,559
But I don't understand

120
00:10:51,559 --> 00:10:53,840
why they want to do that.

121
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:55,320
Are they also angry with Fan Xian

122
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:57,200
and anxious to avenge
Guo Baokun's injuries?

123
00:10:58,919 --> 00:11:00,200
I'd never do such a thing

124
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:01,080
for Guo Baokun.

125
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:02,919
I believe what you said,

126
00:11:02,919 --> 00:11:06,320
but I really can't think of anyone else

127
00:11:07,159 --> 00:11:08,480
who has a grudge against Fan Xian

128
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:10,519
in the capital city.

129
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:13,799
Chengze, do you know gossip
is a fearful thing?

130
00:11:14,919 --> 00:11:16,080
Do you think

131
00:11:16,360 --> 00:11:18,120
murder is a solution to problems?

132
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:19,000
Of course not.

133
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:20,960
There are so many complicated things
in the world.

134
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:22,480
How could they be solved by murder?

135
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:24,480
I agree.

136
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:27,240
I think murder is
a solution to problems.

137
00:11:28,279 --> 00:11:30,000
You can kill Fan Xian
if he's in the way.

138
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:32,440
You can kill officials
if they suspect you.

139
00:11:32,879 --> 00:11:34,960
You can kill the whole staff
of the Investigator's Office

140
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:37,159
if they make detailed inquires.

141
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:39,159
You can also kill me

142
00:11:39,720 --> 00:11:41,039
if I'm suspicious.

143
00:11:42,039 --> 00:11:44,440
Murder seems like a solution
to problems,

144
00:11:44,600 --> 00:11:48,039
but only the unpardonably wicked
would turn to that.

145
00:11:48,559 --> 00:11:49,759
I'd be destroyed by heaven and earth

146
00:11:50,279 --> 00:11:51,159
if I meant to do that.

147
00:11:51,639 --> 00:11:52,720
So would I.

148
00:11:53,039 --> 00:11:54,840
Then stop sounding each other out.

149
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:56,519
How can you rule the world

150
00:11:56,759 --> 00:11:58,960
if you aren't large-hearted enough?

151
00:12:01,919 --> 00:12:04,159
You despised the national law

152
00:12:04,279 --> 00:12:06,679
by acting in such a foolhardy manner.

153
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:08,799
You can leave.

154
00:12:09,279 --> 00:12:09,799
Your Majesty,

155
00:12:11,559 --> 00:12:12,879
here is a secret report
from the Investigator's Office.

156
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:19,159
They want to set Cheng Jushu free?

157
00:12:19,799 --> 00:12:20,240
Yes.

158
00:12:20,519 --> 00:12:21,320
Did Fan Xian know that?

159
00:12:21,559 --> 00:12:22,679
Not yet.

160
00:12:23,519 --> 00:12:24,440
Then tell him.

161
00:12:24,919 --> 00:12:25,759
Yes, Your Majesty.

162
00:12:53,120 --> 00:12:53,600
Thank you.

163
00:12:58,159 --> 00:12:58,879
I must leave.

164
00:12:59,639 --> 00:13:00,360
where are you going?

165
00:13:01,759 --> 00:13:03,159
Teng Zijing died because of me.

166
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:04,919
His wife and son

167
00:13:07,600 --> 00:13:08,679
still don't know about that.

168
00:13:12,080 --> 00:13:12,639
My Lady!

169
00:13:15,399 --> 00:13:17,120
Lady Fan Ruoruo is here.

170
00:13:19,559 --> 00:13:20,399
Let her in.

171
00:13:20,840 --> 00:13:21,320
Got it.

172
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:30,080
Brother, Cheng Jushu will be set free.

173
00:13:41,759 --> 00:13:42,240
Your Excellency.

174
00:13:42,559 --> 00:13:43,240
Where is Cheng Jushu?

175
00:13:43,759 --> 00:13:45,279
In the dungeon.

176
00:13:45,279 --> 00:13:46,320
Have you found out the one behind this?

177
00:13:47,159 --> 00:13:47,840
He said nothing.

178
00:13:48,039 --> 00:13:48,879
What will you do with him?

179
00:13:49,639 --> 00:13:50,120
Your Excellency.

180
00:13:50,360 --> 00:13:50,960
Answer me!

181
00:13:52,120 --> 00:13:53,000
He'll be sent out of town.

182
00:13:53,159 --> 00:13:53,720
And then?

183
00:13:54,879 --> 00:13:55,759
He'll be set free.

184
00:13:57,720 --> 00:13:58,600
Who made the decision?

185
00:13:58,840 --> 00:14:00,039
Generally, when the Head is not
in the capital city,

186
00:14:00,440 --> 00:14:01,399
Mr. Zhu Ge,

187
00:14:01,480 --> 00:14:02,399
director of the First Division,

188
00:14:02,440 --> 00:14:03,519
will take care of all matters related.

189
00:14:03,559 --> 00:14:04,159
Take me to see him.

190
00:14:04,279 --> 00:14:04,759
Your Excellency.

191
00:14:04,960 --> 00:14:06,000
Take me to see him.

192
00:14:07,200 --> 00:14:08,000
Please follow me.

193
00:14:09,720 --> 00:14:11,600
The Investigator's Office
is divided into eight divisions,

194
00:14:11,840 --> 00:14:12,639
each of which performs
its own functions.

195
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:14,519
The First Division is responsible for

196
00:14:14,879 --> 00:14:15,879
supervising officials
in the capital city.

197
00:14:16,120 --> 00:14:17,440
This is the most important unit.

198
00:14:19,440 --> 00:14:21,320
Zhu Ge has followed the Head for years.

199
00:14:21,960 --> 00:14:23,879
He's powerful and influential.

200
00:14:25,440 --> 00:14:26,840
And he's particularly severe.

201
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:27,440
Right here.

202
00:14:27,799 --> 00:14:28,200
Your Excellency,

203
00:14:28,960 --> 00:14:29,840
please be cautious
with your words and actions

204
00:14:30,039 --> 00:14:31,799
when you see him.

205
00:14:38,480 --> 00:14:39,159
Your Excellency,

206
00:14:41,039 --> 00:14:42,519
Mr. Fan Xian, a disciple of Master Fei

207
00:14:43,159 --> 00:14:44,399
of the Investigator's Office
in a short time?

208
00:14:44,519 --> 00:14:46,200
wants to see you.

209
00:14:46,759 --> 00:14:47,399
I'm not available.

210
00:14:49,080 --> 00:14:49,519
Your Excellency.

211
00:14:52,320 --> 00:14:52,919
Your Excellency.

212
00:14:55,519 --> 00:14:56,559
You want to set Cheng Jushu free?

213
00:14:58,919 --> 00:15:00,679
Among the eight directors
of the Investigator's Office,

214
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:01,960
Fei Jie ranks third

215
00:15:02,279 --> 00:15:04,399
as for his capabilities,

216
00:15:05,720 --> 00:15:06,799
but I look down upon him most

217
00:15:07,600 --> 00:15:09,759
as for the way he behaves.

218
00:15:10,559 --> 00:15:13,080
He can't make a clear distinction
between public and private interests

219
00:15:13,279 --> 00:15:15,639
or between the important
and the less important.

220
00:15:16,399 --> 00:15:17,879
As his disciple,

221
00:15:18,240 --> 00:15:20,679
you'd better not follow him
in this respect.

222
00:15:20,679 --> 00:15:21,879
Why do you want to set Cheng Jushu free?

223
00:15:22,279 --> 00:15:23,960
You just need to obey orders.

224
00:15:24,120 --> 00:15:25,039
Don't ask unnecessary questions.

225
00:15:28,399 --> 00:15:29,720
Of the Investigator's Office
in a short time?

226
00:15:30,559 --> 00:15:31,679
I don't need to follow
any of the eight directors.

227
00:15:31,679 --> 00:15:33,120
I have the same seniority as you.

228
00:15:33,519 --> 00:15:34,759
The token is not false, right?

229
00:15:36,960 --> 00:15:37,559
Right.

230
00:15:38,240 --> 00:15:39,919
Okay. Let me repeat it.

231
00:15:41,600 --> 00:15:43,080
Why do you want to set Cheng Jushu free?

232
00:15:48,919 --> 00:15:50,080
According to an urgent report
from the Ministry of War,

233
00:15:51,960 --> 00:15:55,039
there is an emergency deployment
of armies at the northern border.

234
00:15:55,120 --> 00:15:57,039
A war may break out at any moment.

235
00:15:57,279 --> 00:15:58,960
Nanqing has planning a war against Beiqi

236
00:15:59,200 --> 00:16:00,279
for a long time,

237
00:16:00,600 --> 00:16:02,200
but the timing of making war

238
00:16:02,559 --> 00:16:04,840
has to be decided by us.

239
00:16:05,200 --> 00:16:07,240
How is it related to Cheng Jushu?

240
00:16:07,720 --> 00:16:10,279
Cheng Jushu is a martial arts master
from Beiqi.

241
00:16:10,840 --> 00:16:12,200
If he dies in the capital city,

242
00:16:12,679 --> 00:16:14,279
it may give Beiqi an excuse.

243
00:16:14,720 --> 00:16:16,960
The national plans will be destroyed

244
00:16:17,279 --> 00:16:19,120
in case they attack us at this time.

245
00:16:19,480 --> 00:16:20,240
In case?

246
00:16:22,759 --> 00:16:24,120
That's why you made that decision?

247
00:16:24,200 --> 00:16:26,759
One of Cheng Jushu's friends

248
00:16:27,200 --> 00:16:28,799
is a general of Beiqi.

249
00:16:29,639 --> 00:16:30,559
He promised

250
00:16:30,840 --> 00:16:32,720
he'd provide us

251
00:16:33,159 --> 00:16:34,840
with details about the deployment

252
00:16:35,240 --> 00:16:37,000
of forces at the border

253
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:38,200
if we keep Cheng Jushu safe.

254
00:16:38,720 --> 00:16:40,320
So, you did business with him.

255
00:16:40,600 --> 00:16:41,879
No matter what we do,

256
00:16:42,039 --> 00:16:44,000
we have to put
the country's interests first.

257
00:16:44,320 --> 00:16:46,200
But if we can only win at the
sacrifice of the innocent people,

258
00:16:46,200 --> 00:16:47,799
then what's the meaning of it!

259
00:16:47,879 --> 00:16:48,960
It's a matter
concerning national safety.

260
00:16:48,960 --> 00:16:50,679
It's not up to you.

261
00:16:50,720 --> 00:16:51,720
A life for a life.

262
00:16:51,840 --> 00:16:53,279
This is the law.

263
00:16:53,279 --> 00:16:54,159
It's just a guard

264
00:16:54,159 --> 00:16:55,360
that was killed.

265
00:16:58,440 --> 00:17:00,600
Just a guard?

266
00:17:06,920 --> 00:17:07,759
Your Excellency,

267
00:17:09,680 --> 00:17:11,559
the stone tablet at the gate says

268
00:17:12,279 --> 00:17:13,759
men are created equal

269
00:17:14,359 --> 00:17:15,720
and there is neither lowliness
nor nobleness,

270
00:17:16,440 --> 00:17:18,720
on which the Investigator's Office
is based.

271
00:17:20,240 --> 00:17:21,400
A guard is also a man.

272
00:17:22,599 --> 00:17:24,359
He's a father.

273
00:17:26,640 --> 00:17:28,640
He's a husband.

274
00:17:30,640 --> 00:17:33,039
He's the only one his family
can depend on.

275
00:17:34,759 --> 00:17:36,839
The victim is dead,

276
00:17:37,039 --> 00:17:38,759
but the murderer will be set free.

277
00:17:40,559 --> 00:17:41,519
Where is the national law?

278
00:17:44,759 --> 00:17:46,240
Where is the justice?

