560
00:31:16,799 --> 00:31:18,240
Now that Fan Jie
is not in the capital city,

561
00:31:18,400 --> 00:31:19,599
the Third Division could do nothing

562
00:31:19,720 --> 00:31:20,599
without a leader.

563
00:31:21,160 --> 00:31:22,400
I'm much obliged to them.

564
00:31:23,119 --> 00:31:23,759
Fan Xian,

565
00:31:24,440 --> 00:31:26,119
you ruined our plan to attack Beiqi.

566
00:31:26,400 --> 00:31:27,799
Nobody can save you.

567
00:31:28,000 --> 00:31:29,319
Have you thought of it

568
00:31:29,400 --> 00:31:30,799
when you killed Cheng Jushu?

569
00:31:32,599 --> 00:31:33,640
Your Excellency, hold on.

570
00:31:34,279 --> 00:31:34,839
Wait a moment.

571
00:31:35,640 --> 00:31:36,160
Well,

572
00:31:36,559 --> 00:31:38,279
Even a clerk dares to stop me?

573
00:31:39,279 --> 00:31:40,119
Don't get me wrong.

574
00:31:40,759 --> 00:31:42,559
How could I dare to do that?

575
00:31:42,559 --> 00:31:44,039
I'll never stop you.

576
00:31:46,559 --> 00:31:47,359
Get out of the way!

577
00:31:47,759 --> 00:31:48,920
Hold on.

578
00:31:49,359 --> 00:31:50,880
Believe it or not. I'll fire you!

579
00:31:52,759 --> 00:31:53,319
Your Excellency,

580
00:31:53,640 --> 00:31:55,960
Fan Xian did something good to Nanqing!

581
00:31:56,920 --> 00:31:58,079
Are you crazy?

582
00:31:58,680 --> 00:31:59,400
Your Excellency,

583
00:32:00,319 --> 00:32:02,119
could you tell me which general of Beiqi

584
00:32:02,519 --> 00:32:04,599
wants to exchange their military plan

585
00:32:04,599 --> 00:32:05,640
for Cheng Jushu?

586
00:32:05,960 --> 00:32:07,559
It's none of your business!

587
00:32:11,319 --> 00:32:12,279
Your Excellency, check this out!

588
00:32:13,640 --> 00:32:14,359
What's this?

589
00:32:15,039 --> 00:32:16,240
It's a file

590
00:32:16,640 --> 00:32:18,079
on Cheng Jushu's life.

591
00:32:18,519 --> 00:32:19,799
What on earth do you want to say?

592
00:32:20,519 --> 00:32:22,640
I've read it carefully.

593
00:32:23,079 --> 00:32:25,039
Cheng Jushu is unsociable and eccentric.

594
00:32:25,279 --> 00:32:26,240
He's obstinate and unruly.

595
00:32:26,480 --> 00:32:27,400
He doesn't have any friend

596
00:32:27,400 --> 00:32:28,759
who serves in the army.

597
00:32:29,720 --> 00:32:30,319
Besides,

598
00:32:31,039 --> 00:32:32,319
most of the high-ranking
military officers

599
00:32:32,400 --> 00:32:33,519
of Beiqi at the border

600
00:32:33,720 --> 00:32:35,480
think poorly of him

601
00:32:35,519 --> 00:32:37,160
and even hold grudges against him.

602
00:32:37,680 --> 00:32:38,960
In this case,

603
00:32:39,440 --> 00:32:40,960
who would want

604
00:32:41,079 --> 00:32:42,759
to exchange their military plan

605
00:32:42,839 --> 00:32:45,160
for Cheng Jushu's life?

606
00:32:50,039 --> 00:32:51,359
They aim to give you false information

607
00:32:52,039 --> 00:32:53,640
in the name of saving Cheng Jushu.

608
00:32:53,960 --> 00:32:56,000
Your Excellency Fan,
you're really clever.

609
00:32:56,440 --> 00:32:58,599
I agree with you.

610
00:32:59,559 --> 00:33:01,960
They want to take this opportunity

611
00:33:02,359 --> 00:33:04,240
to send us false information.

612
00:33:04,319 --> 00:33:05,039
Once we go to war,

613
00:33:05,160 --> 00:33:06,200
such disinformation

614
00:33:06,359 --> 00:33:08,839
will make us fall into deadly traps.

615
00:33:09,480 --> 00:33:10,200
So,

616
00:33:10,680 --> 00:33:12,519
by killing Cheng Jushu,

617
00:33:12,839 --> 00:33:14,240
His Excellency Fan did a good job

618
00:33:14,559 --> 00:33:16,839
instead of making a mistake.

619
00:33:19,119 --> 00:33:21,400
Your Excellency, did you hear that?

620
00:33:27,759 --> 00:33:29,440
Your Excellency,

621
00:33:29,799 --> 00:33:32,480
His Excellency Fan
set things right accidentally

622
00:33:32,960 --> 00:33:34,680
by doing that.

623
00:33:34,960 --> 00:33:38,000
Please give him a lesser punishment.

624
00:33:41,359 --> 00:33:42,079
Wang Qinian,

625
00:33:43,240 --> 00:33:44,519
you've spared no effort

626
00:33:44,920 --> 00:33:46,720
to save Fan Xian.

627
00:33:47,920 --> 00:33:49,359
That's a strong word.

628
00:33:49,599 --> 00:33:51,920
I'm taking the matter on its merits.

629
00:33:52,359 --> 00:33:53,920
Do you think you're the only one

630
00:33:54,359 --> 00:33:55,799
who has noticed that?

631
00:33:59,759 --> 00:34:02,279
It's a war of nations.
We all know its importance.

632
00:34:02,559 --> 00:34:03,640
How could I not find out

633
00:34:03,640 --> 00:34:05,480
Cheng Jushu's background?

634
00:34:06,240 --> 00:34:06,599
Then,

635
00:34:06,599 --> 00:34:07,920
Answer me.

636
00:34:08,159 --> 00:34:10,159
Why do you think

637
00:34:10,159 --> 00:34:11,800
I want to exchange Cheng Jushu's life

638
00:34:11,800 --> 00:34:13,119
for that disinformation?

639
00:34:19,039 --> 00:34:21,840
Did you turn their trick to our own use?

640
00:34:22,519 --> 00:34:24,280
You want to make them believe

641
00:34:24,719 --> 00:34:25,440
You're fooled?

642
00:34:25,599 --> 00:34:27,719
By then we'd know

643
00:34:27,719 --> 00:34:29,880
everything about them clearly.

644
00:34:30,079 --> 00:34:31,559
It'd be easy to defeat them.

645
00:34:31,559 --> 00:34:33,199
But Fan Xian killed Cheng Jushu.

646
00:34:33,400 --> 00:34:35,000
He's destroyed our plan!

647
00:34:35,159 --> 00:34:35,760
Well, he...

648
00:34:35,760 --> 00:34:39,239
It's understandable, anyway.

649
00:34:39,480 --> 00:34:41,960
Since when could the Investigator's Office
stand such a matter?

650
00:34:46,960 --> 00:34:49,280
Fan Xian, have a guess.

651
00:34:49,519 --> 00:34:51,639
Who else would try to save you?

652
00:34:54,719 --> 00:34:55,760
I'm a people person.

653
00:34:56,239 --> 00:34:56,960
I can't guess it.

654
00:34:59,639 --> 00:35:01,239
Head is not in the capital city.

655
00:35:01,840 --> 00:35:03,639
Nobody can save you.

656
00:35:04,000 --> 00:35:04,679
Take him away!

657
00:35:04,880 --> 00:35:05,280
Wait.

658
00:35:06,400 --> 00:35:07,000
Hold on.

659
00:35:14,280 --> 00:35:15,480
Yan Ruohai,

660
00:35:51,920 --> 00:35:53,440
I've thought of many people,

661
00:35:53,639 --> 00:35:55,079
but I didn't expect it'd be you.

662
00:35:56,280 --> 00:35:57,239
Who is he?

663
00:35:58,280 --> 00:35:59,880
The Investigator's Office
is divided into eight divisions.

664
00:36:00,159 --> 00:36:02,000
This is His Excellency Yan Ruohai,
director of the Fourth Division

665
00:36:02,199 --> 00:36:04,320
that's responsible for supervising
officials outside the capital city

666
00:36:04,519 --> 00:36:07,599
and carrying on

667
00:36:07,599 --> 00:36:08,519
Your Excellency.

668
00:36:09,840 --> 00:36:11,719
The name sounds familiar to me.

669
00:36:15,159 --> 00:36:17,760
My son was demoted and left
the capital city because of you.

670
00:36:19,159 --> 00:36:20,320
Yan Bingyun is your son.

671
00:36:25,519 --> 00:36:26,280
Let him go.

672
00:36:30,159 --> 00:36:32,039
Bingyun lurks in the capital of Beiqi

673
00:36:32,159 --> 00:36:33,239
it's hard to survive.

674
00:36:33,320 --> 00:36:34,480
It's all his fault.

675
00:36:34,719 --> 00:36:35,400
I know.

676
00:36:35,679 --> 00:36:36,840
Why did you help him?

677
00:36:38,039 --> 00:36:39,360
I'm just here to pass on a message.

678
00:36:40,199 --> 00:36:41,440
Head is not in the capital city.

679
00:36:41,800 --> 00:36:42,960
From whom is the message?

680
00:36:59,000 --> 00:37:00,079
It's an imperial decree.

681
00:37:04,159 --> 00:37:06,039
Aren't you going to kneel down?

682
00:37:07,400 --> 00:37:08,599
I'm listening with respectful attention.

683
00:37:11,719 --> 00:37:13,679
Wang Qinian, what's going on?

684
00:37:14,480 --> 00:37:15,480
Kneel down.

685
00:37:15,480 --> 00:37:16,159
I can't.

686
00:37:16,159 --> 00:37:17,280
I'm tied up.

687
00:37:18,920 --> 00:37:19,559
Your Excellency.

688
00:37:19,559 --> 00:37:20,159
How dare you!

689
00:37:26,880 --> 00:37:28,840
Forget about it.
I don't want to read it.

690
00:37:28,920 --> 00:37:29,599
Look at it yourself.

691
00:37:30,159 --> 00:37:31,159
It's simple.

692
00:37:31,519 --> 00:37:32,519
His Majesty asked you
to let Fan Xian go.

693
00:37:33,280 --> 00:37:34,079
I will obey the order.

694
00:37:43,159 --> 00:37:43,599
Guards!

695
00:37:44,639 --> 00:37:45,280
Untie the ropes.

696
00:37:52,760 --> 00:37:53,719
Return the token to him.

697
00:38:01,519 --> 00:38:02,320
You're free to go.

698
00:38:03,000 --> 00:38:03,800
Thank you, Your Excellency.

699
00:38:04,119 --> 00:38:05,360
Even if those things
hadn't happened to my son,

700
00:38:06,079 --> 00:38:07,480
I don't like you

701
00:38:08,079 --> 00:38:09,239
because of your casual attitude.

702
00:38:10,880 --> 00:38:11,960
I helped to save you,

703
00:38:12,800 --> 00:38:13,880
but I still look down upon you.

704
00:38:14,599 --> 00:38:16,599
So, don't thank me. Go home.

705
00:38:27,079 --> 00:38:28,000
Wang Qinian,

706
00:38:29,000 --> 00:38:29,880
walk me home.

707
00:38:32,480 --> 00:38:33,679
I have the same seniority as him.

708
00:38:36,480 --> 00:38:38,920
Your Excellencies,

709
00:38:39,800 --> 00:38:41,559
let me drive His Excellency Fan away.

710
00:38:44,800 --> 00:38:45,280
Let's go.

711
00:38:46,159 --> 00:38:47,320
Your Excellency, see you around.

712
00:38:50,719 --> 00:38:51,239
Your Excellency.

713
00:39:09,360 --> 00:39:10,079
Your Excellency,

714
00:39:10,679 --> 00:39:11,559
tell me

715
00:39:12,000 --> 00:39:13,360
how you made His Excellency Yan Ruohai

716
00:39:13,360 --> 00:39:14,800
your friend from your enemy.

717
00:39:15,239 --> 00:39:16,159
I didn't know him.

718
00:39:17,199 --> 00:39:19,320
Do you know His Majesty?

719
00:39:20,079 --> 00:39:20,800
What do you think?

720
00:39:22,480 --> 00:39:23,639
So I just don't get it.

721
00:39:24,599 --> 00:39:26,440
You killed Cheng Jushu

722
00:39:26,440 --> 00:39:27,280
at the gate
of the Investigator's Office,

723
00:39:27,480 --> 00:39:29,920
but His Majesty ordered them
to set you free.

724
00:39:29,960 --> 00:39:30,679
Why?

725
00:39:31,559 --> 00:39:32,800
Because I did it in public.

726
00:39:33,760 --> 00:39:34,559
What?

727
00:39:35,840 --> 00:39:37,480
If I killed Cheng Jushu in secret,

728
00:39:37,719 --> 00:39:38,880
I'd be punished.

729
00:39:39,400 --> 00:39:40,519
On the contrary,

730
00:39:41,519 --> 00:39:42,599
I'd be safe since I did it in public.

731
00:39:43,960 --> 00:39:44,679
Why?

732
00:39:46,639 --> 00:39:47,719
Four words.

733
00:39:51,880 --> 00:39:52,920
People will talk.

734
00:39:53,599 --> 00:39:55,880
That's why His Majesty did that.

735
00:39:56,880 --> 00:39:57,840
Everyone is talking
about the assassination attempt

736
00:39:58,199 --> 00:39:59,400
that was carried out yesterday.

737
00:39:59,920 --> 00:40:00,840
Today, Fan Xian

738
00:40:01,039 --> 00:40:02,719
killed Cheng Jushu in public.

739
00:40:03,519 --> 00:40:04,679
Everyone knows that

740
00:40:05,079 --> 00:40:06,000
he did it to take revenge.

741
00:40:06,519 --> 00:40:07,599
So what?

742
00:40:08,400 --> 00:40:10,000
Cheng Jushu is
a martial arts master from Beiqi.

743
00:40:11,559 --> 00:40:12,119
Your Excellency,

744
00:40:12,800 --> 00:40:13,719
Nanqing

745
00:40:14,159 --> 00:40:15,719
is the world's leading power.

746
00:40:16,159 --> 00:40:17,480
People here are always
proud and confident.

747
00:40:18,639 --> 00:40:21,079
Now, a gifted scholar in Nanqing killed

748
00:40:21,480 --> 00:40:22,760
a martial arts master from Beiqi.

749
00:40:23,280 --> 00:40:25,280
Isn't it a story passed
on with approval?

750
00:40:27,800 --> 00:40:29,440
What will the common people think

751
00:40:29,880 --> 00:40:30,880
if we put Fan Xian into prison?

752
00:40:34,400 --> 00:40:35,360
But Fan Xian is also

753
00:40:36,159 --> 00:40:38,119
he broke the law anyway.

754
00:40:38,719 --> 00:40:41,280
The war will begin soon. It's important to
win support from the common people.

755
00:40:41,800 --> 00:40:43,400
What His Majesty wants to protect

756
00:40:44,039 --> 00:40:45,400
is not Fan Xian

757
00:40:45,760 --> 00:40:46,760
but people's determination to win

758
00:40:47,199 --> 00:40:48,239
and their fighting will.

759
00:40:52,239 --> 00:40:53,360
I see.

760
00:40:53,920 --> 00:40:55,960
That's why you wanted
to kill Cheng Jushu

761
00:40:55,960 --> 00:40:56,960
in broad daylight.

762
00:40:57,400 --> 00:40:58,519
When I did that,

763
00:40:58,599 --> 00:40:59,719
I just wanted to take revenge.

764
00:41:00,079 --> 00:41:00,800
I didn't figure out the whole thing

765
00:41:01,000 --> 00:41:02,239
until it all had happened.

766
00:41:03,039 --> 00:41:03,719
It means

767
00:41:03,960 --> 00:41:05,760
Heaven rewards the good.

768
00:41:05,760 --> 00:41:07,519
What you did conforms
to the will of Heaven,

769
00:41:07,639 --> 00:41:08,639
so you turned ill luck into good.

770
00:41:08,760 --> 00:41:09,199
Wang,

771
00:41:10,559 --> 00:41:11,239
do me another favor.

772
00:41:11,960 --> 00:41:14,000
You've already killed him.

773
00:41:14,039 --> 00:41:15,159
I haven't found the one
behind the scenes.

774
00:41:15,440 --> 00:41:16,079
It's not over yet.

775
00:41:16,599 --> 00:41:18,400
But Cheng Jushu is dead.

776
00:41:18,400 --> 00:41:19,400
There were also
two female assassinators.

777
00:41:19,920 --> 00:41:20,519
They're dead too.

778
00:41:20,519 --> 00:41:21,239
It doesn't matter.

779
00:41:21,519 --> 00:41:22,239
Find out their background.

780
00:41:22,639 --> 00:41:23,079
Your Excellency,

781
00:41:24,079 --> 00:41:26,280
it's confidential.
I don't have the right to...

782
00:41:30,280 --> 00:41:30,800
Fine.

783
00:41:31,320 --> 00:41:33,159
For truth and justice,

784
00:41:33,639 --> 00:41:35,079
it's my bounden duty.

785
00:42:37,320 --> 00:42:38,360
How is it going at you side?

786
00:42:41,519 --> 00:42:43,360
This is the token
of the secret agent from Beiqi.

787
00:42:44,239 --> 00:42:44,840
Token?

788
00:42:45,440 --> 00:42:46,599
Beiqi has secret agents

789
00:42:46,599 --> 00:42:47,800
that lurk in Nanqing.

790
00:42:48,000 --> 00:42:50,320
They use tokens like this
to deploy subordinates

791
00:42:50,440 --> 00:42:51,360
and conduct activities.

792
00:42:52,159 --> 00:42:53,159
In that sense,

793
00:42:54,000 --> 00:42:55,599
Cheng Jushu is a Beiqi secret agent.

794
00:42:55,760 --> 00:42:56,679
I'm afraid so!

795
00:43:02,880 --> 00:43:04,360
What an honor to me!

796
00:43:05,840 --> 00:43:07,320
This unknown big hand

797
00:43:07,360 --> 00:43:08,400
unites Beiqi

798
00:43:09,119 --> 00:43:11,000
just to kill me.

799
00:43:11,639 --> 00:43:12,159
Your Excellency.

800
00:43:13,199 --> 00:43:14,239
It's getting more and more complicated.

801
00:43:14,760 --> 00:43:15,400
Do we still need to continue with it?

802
00:43:15,599 --> 00:43:16,119
Investigate!

803
00:43:18,000 --> 00:43:19,480
We can't let Teng Zijing
die for nothing.

804
00:43:21,639 --> 00:43:22,679
I'll never give up

805
00:43:23,760 --> 00:43:24,840
before finding out the true killer.

806
00:43:25,119 --> 00:43:26,400
Why did Cheng Jushu
and the female assassinators

807
00:43:26,639 --> 00:43:28,079
choose Niulan Street
for the assassination?

808
00:43:29,280 --> 00:43:31,480
You were heading towards Joy Tsin House

809
00:43:32,320 --> 00:43:33,920
and would undoubtedly
pass by Niulan Street.

810
00:43:34,159 --> 00:43:35,440
How did they know it?

811
00:43:36,519 --> 00:43:37,639
Perhaps they didn't.

812
00:43:37,800 --> 00:43:39,239
They just followed secretly

813
00:43:39,360 --> 00:43:40,760
and planned to do it by chance.

814
00:43:40,880 --> 00:43:41,480
Impossible!

815
00:43:43,599 --> 00:43:45,840
Two assassinators attacked from front
and back respectively that day.

816
00:43:45,840 --> 00:43:47,159
Cheng Jushu hid at the back of the wall.

817
00:43:47,599 --> 00:43:48,320
It was an ambush

818
00:43:48,320 --> 00:43:49,280
well planned in advance.

819
00:43:50,199 --> 00:43:51,840
They had known I would
pass by Niulan Street well before it.

820
00:43:52,760 --> 00:43:53,719
Who else knew

821
00:43:53,760 --> 00:43:54,719
you were going to Joy Tsin House?

822
00:43:55,199 --> 00:43:56,920
The person who made the appointment
with me naturally knew it.

823
00:43:57,920 --> 00:43:58,840
The Second Prince?

824
00:44:02,360 --> 00:44:03,440
He is under too much suspicion

825
00:44:03,440 --> 00:44:04,320
to do it

826
00:44:04,360 --> 00:44:05,079
which makes it seem deliberate.

827
00:44:06,119 --> 00:44:07,039
Then there isn't any more suspect left.

828
00:44:08,039 --> 00:44:08,639
Aren't you aware

829
00:44:09,239 --> 00:44:10,440
since it was an appointment,

830
00:44:11,320 --> 00:44:12,599
Joy Tsin House would need to

831
00:44:12,599 --> 00:44:13,480
prepare the banquet in advance.

832
00:44:14,679 --> 00:44:15,880
It's the people from Joy Tsin House?!

833
00:44:17,360 --> 00:44:18,320
They also knew

834
00:44:18,320 --> 00:44:19,519
I would pass by Niulan Street.

835
00:44:20,280 --> 00:44:21,239
But Miss Si Lili and you

836
00:44:21,239 --> 00:44:22,199
like each other so much.

837
00:44:22,199 --> 00:44:23,039
People from her side

838
00:44:23,039 --> 00:44:24,039
shouldn't have any problem.

839
00:44:24,199 --> 00:44:25,360
I have no connection

840
00:44:25,360 --> 00:44:26,320
with Si Lili.

841
00:44:27,239 --> 00:44:28,639
In retrospect,

842
00:44:29,559 --> 00:44:30,519
this Miss

843
00:44:30,599 --> 00:44:31,840
doesn't look like

844
00:44:31,840 --> 00:44:32,800
a courtesan in brothel at all.

845
00:44:36,559 --> 00:44:37,559
So we need to go

846
00:44:37,559 --> 00:44:38,800
to Joy Tsin House immediately.

847
00:44:40,599 --> 00:44:41,159
Exactly.

848
00:44:43,239 --> 00:44:43,920
Let me in!

849
00:44:43,920 --> 00:44:44,519
No! No!

850
00:44:44,519 --> 00:44:45,960
Sir, you can't come inside.

851
00:44:45,960 --> 00:44:47,039
Why not?

852
00:44:47,679 --> 00:44:49,119
Listen!

853
00:44:49,519 --> 00:44:50,559
I made an appointment

854
00:44:50,559 --> 00:44:52,440
with Miss Yunjian a long time ago.

855
00:44:53,039 --> 00:44:54,159
What's the reason not to let me in?

856
00:44:54,639 --> 00:44:55,559
There is no reason.

857
00:44:55,760 --> 00:44:56,440
I must get in!

858
00:44:56,440 --> 00:44:56,920
Sir!

859
00:44:57,920 --> 00:44:58,559
Sir!

860
00:44:58,679 --> 00:44:59,880
You probably don't know that

861
00:45:00,000 --> 00:45:01,719
Miss Si Lili's boat

862
00:45:01,719 --> 00:45:02,679
has been burnt.

863
00:45:03,559 --> 00:45:04,679
The government is investigating

864
00:45:04,679 --> 00:45:05,719
the cause of the fire.

865
00:45:05,719 --> 00:45:06,880
No one is allowed to go inside.

866
00:45:07,280 --> 00:45:08,800
Please forgive us.

867
00:45:08,800 --> 00:45:09,480
Please forgive me.

868
00:45:09,480 --> 00:45:10,599
-Go. -Go. Go.

869
00:45:10,920 --> 00:45:11,320
Wait!

870
00:45:12,039 --> 00:45:13,960
You said the boat got burnt?

871
00:45:13,960 --> 00:45:14,760
When did that happen?

872
00:45:15,880 --> 00:45:17,760
Sir, it was this noon.

873
00:45:19,360 --> 00:45:20,079
It's such a pity

874
00:45:20,320 --> 00:45:21,559
that a good boat got burnt

875
00:45:21,719 --> 00:45:23,320
to ashes.

876
00:45:23,679 --> 00:45:24,679
Where is Si Lili now?

877
00:45:25,679 --> 00:45:26,239
She's gone?

878
00:45:26,639 --> 00:45:28,239
Someone saw her going out of the city.

879
00:45:29,559 --> 00:45:30,480
She must be frustrated

880
00:45:30,840 --> 00:45:32,079
that the boat got burnt.

881
00:45:33,719 --> 00:45:34,280
Gentlemen,

882
00:45:34,519 --> 00:45:35,800
please come some other day.

883
00:45:35,800 --> 00:45:36,360
Please...

884
00:45:36,360 --> 00:45:37,440
Excuse us, please!

885
00:45:41,079 --> 00:45:42,239
There is no clue

886
00:45:42,239 --> 00:45:43,519
up to this point.

887
00:45:44,079 --> 00:45:44,559
Your Excellency,

888
00:45:46,559 --> 00:45:47,920
if we can find Si Lili,

889
00:45:48,320 --> 00:45:49,760
there should be some clue.

890
00:45:50,920 --> 00:45:51,920
Didn't you hear it?

891
00:45:51,920 --> 00:45:52,880
She's gone for quite a while.

892
00:45:52,880 --> 00:45:53,440
How do we find her?!

893
00:45:57,039 --> 00:45:59,239
Your Excellency may not know that

894
00:45:59,559 --> 00:46:00,639
the Investigator's Office

895
00:46:00,960 --> 00:46:02,880
has two masters of hunting.

896
00:46:03,760 --> 00:46:04,480
One of them

897
00:46:04,840 --> 00:46:06,039
is called Zong Zhui.

898
00:46:06,400 --> 00:46:07,519
Generally, he follows the Head.

899
00:46:07,719 --> 00:46:08,960
He is not in the capital city now.

900
00:46:11,239 --> 00:46:12,679
As for the other one,

901
00:46:15,719 --> 00:46:17,559
would you like to have a guess

902
00:46:17,920 --> 00:46:20,320
who the other guy is?

903
00:46:25,519 --> 00:46:26,719
Is that you?

904
00:46:28,119 --> 00:46:29,320
I'm afraid yes.

905
00:46:30,679 --> 00:46:31,760
It's surprising

906
00:46:31,920 --> 00:46:33,199
that you are just a clerk
with that skill.

907
00:46:34,039 --> 00:46:36,039
Being a clerk is pretty good.

908
00:46:36,440 --> 00:46:38,639
It runs no risk
and therefore super safe.

909
00:46:40,239 --> 00:46:40,960
Why do you help me?

910
00:46:42,199 --> 00:46:42,800
Your Excellency,

911
00:46:43,840 --> 00:46:46,280
I'm driven out

912
00:46:46,360 --> 00:46:47,440
by the Investigator's Office now.

913
00:46:47,559 --> 00:46:49,320
But my whole family

914
00:46:49,840 --> 00:46:51,199
still needs sustenance.

915
00:46:51,519 --> 00:46:53,400
I learned that by working for you,

916
00:46:53,519 --> 00:46:55,119
I can earn 50 taels of silver a month,

917
00:46:55,639 --> 00:46:56,800
and there is land and ox.

918
00:47:01,079 --> 00:47:02,280
If you can really hunt her down for me,

919
00:47:02,280 --> 00:47:03,440
I'll give you 10 extra pigs.

920
00:47:03,760 --> 00:47:04,599
Fantastic!

921
00:47:05,039 --> 00:47:05,960
Your Excellency,

922
00:47:06,440 --> 00:47:07,159
my girl

923
00:47:07,320 --> 00:47:09,119
loves pork belly best.

924
00:47:09,639 --> 00:47:10,719
Are you really able to hunt her down?

925
00:47:11,280 --> 00:47:13,360
That's not a problem to me.

926
00:47:13,480 --> 00:47:14,719
The problem lies in you.

927
00:47:15,400 --> 00:47:15,920
What do you mean?

928
00:47:16,199 --> 00:47:18,039
Si Lili left the capital city so timely.

929
00:47:19,119 --> 00:47:19,760
She could most likely

930
00:47:20,480 --> 00:47:21,679
be the Beiqi secret agent

931
00:47:21,679 --> 00:47:23,199
in view of it.

932
00:47:23,599 --> 00:47:24,920
Her escape

933
00:47:25,400 --> 00:47:27,039
must be a plan well in advance

934
00:47:27,039 --> 00:47:28,039
so as to coordinate
with the backup team.

935
00:47:28,320 --> 00:47:29,719
If Your Excellency must hunt her down,

936
00:47:30,239 --> 00:47:31,920
we must go out of the capital city

937
00:47:32,400 --> 00:47:34,559
and run endless risks

938
00:47:35,239 --> 00:47:36,440
to our lives.

939
00:47:36,960 --> 00:47:37,400
Your Excellency,

940
00:47:38,400 --> 00:47:40,320
are you willing to step
on such a dangerous journey?

941
00:47:42,000 --> 00:47:44,360
It was my brother who was murdered.

942
00:47:44,599 --> 00:47:45,199
In this case,

943
00:47:46,079 --> 00:47:48,159
please follow me to go
out of the capital city

944
00:47:48,880 --> 00:47:50,400
and start up this long journey.

945
00:47:54,599 --> 00:47:55,559
Where are you going?

946
00:47:57,280 --> 00:47:57,840
Where did you go?

947
00:47:58,320 --> 00:47:59,239
Aren't we going out of here?

948
00:47:59,440 --> 00:48:00,079
What do you want to do here?

949
00:48:00,440 --> 00:48:02,599
All my equipment is at home.

950
00:48:03,599 --> 00:48:04,880
I need to fetch them.

951
00:48:18,440 --> 00:48:19,280
Is this your house?

952
00:48:21,039 --> 00:48:22,360
Yes, it is.

953
00:48:22,599 --> 00:48:24,519
Why don't you just walk in?

954
00:48:27,480 --> 00:48:30,159
My wife is home.
It's better to be careful.

955
00:48:30,480 --> 00:48:31,159
Wang Qinian,

956
00:48:32,000 --> 00:48:32,719
you're henpecked!

957
00:48:34,559 --> 00:48:35,880
Your Excellency may not know that

958
00:48:36,159 --> 00:48:38,159
my wife has a nickname,

959
00:48:39,639 --> 00:48:42,559
tigress-like Mrs. Wang.

960
00:48:42,719 --> 00:48:43,519
What like?

961
00:48:43,880 --> 00:48:45,199
Tigress.

962
00:48:46,119 --> 00:48:47,719
Si Lili has gone for a while.

963
00:48:48,440 --> 00:48:49,360
Let's hurry up.

964
00:48:49,559 --> 00:48:50,159
It's fine!

965
00:48:50,599 --> 00:48:51,559
It's easier to hunt

966
00:48:51,760 --> 00:48:52,960
in day time.

967
00:48:59,400 --> 00:49:00,320
My wife is deeply asleep.

968
00:49:01,559 --> 00:49:02,079
Excuse me for a while.

969
00:49:03,360 --> 00:49:04,599
I'll be back soon.

970
00:49:05,960 --> 00:49:07,079
Please keep silent, Your Excellency!

971
00:49:24,559 --> 00:49:25,800
Where are you going again, Wang Qinian?

972
00:49:26,039 --> 00:49:27,440
Did you hide money in the case?

973
00:49:27,559 --> 00:49:28,400
Listen to me, darling!

974
00:49:28,800 --> 00:49:30,960
I've got business to do.

975
00:49:51,199 --> 00:49:51,719
Done, Your Excellency!

976
00:49:51,960 --> 00:49:52,760
It's done! Let's go!

977
00:49:56,840 --> 00:49:57,480
Your Excellency! Your Excellency!

978
00:49:57,639 --> 00:49:58,880
Your Excellency! Your Excellency!

979
00:49:59,119 --> 00:49:59,840
Well done!

980
00:50:00,599 --> 00:50:01,639
That's admiring.

981
00:50:06,519 --> 00:50:07,239
Did you just say that

982
00:50:08,079 --> 00:50:09,320
it's easier to hunt in day time?

983
00:50:09,960 --> 00:50:10,480
Exactly.

984
00:50:12,679 --> 00:50:13,679
Then I also have a person to meet.

985
00:50:44,039 --> 00:50:44,840
Why haven't you gone to bed?

986
00:50:46,639 --> 00:50:48,440
I heard that you killed a man
on the street.

987
00:50:51,960 --> 00:50:53,039
I'm not fond of killing people.

988
00:50:53,599 --> 00:50:55,480
That was to avenge Zijing.

989
00:50:56,440 --> 00:50:58,599
Avenging friends is what man should do.

990
00:50:59,000 --> 00:50:59,920
But today,

991
00:51:00,679 --> 00:51:02,199
you're not here to see me.

992
00:51:02,920 --> 00:51:03,599
How could you say that?

993
00:51:04,119 --> 00:51:05,480
You didn't wear the nocturnal costume

994
00:51:06,119 --> 00:51:07,599
or the perfume.

995
00:51:12,119 --> 00:51:12,559
Wan'er.

996
00:51:13,760 --> 00:51:14,639
Si Lili from Joy Tsin House

997
00:51:15,639 --> 00:51:16,679
may have a hand

998
00:51:17,039 --> 00:51:18,079
in the assassination.

999
00:51:19,960 --> 00:51:22,320
She is at large out of the capital city.

1000
00:51:23,679 --> 00:51:24,599
I have to get her back.

1001
00:51:25,559 --> 00:51:26,480
You are leaving soon?

1002
00:51:26,719 --> 00:51:27,960
Yes, but I thought you'll be worried.

1003
00:51:28,119 --> 00:51:28,840
So here I am to say goodbye.

1004
00:51:29,039 --> 00:51:29,719
When will you be back?

1005
00:51:29,800 --> 00:51:30,440
As soon as I get her.

1006
00:51:30,719 --> 00:51:31,639
What if you don't?

1007
00:51:36,960 --> 00:51:37,960
I won't stop you

1008
00:51:38,559 --> 00:51:39,360
from what you want to do,

1009
00:51:41,639 --> 00:51:43,000
but it's impossible for me

1010
00:51:44,000 --> 00:51:44,719
not to worry.

1011
00:51:51,880 --> 00:51:52,400
Wan'er.

1012
00:51:58,920 --> 00:52:00,119
How about a hug before I leave?

1013
00:52:08,519 --> 00:52:11,599
It's dawn. I gotta go.

1014
00:52:26,800 --> 00:52:28,079
I'll be worried every day.

1015
00:52:29,559 --> 00:52:31,039
If you don't want me to,

1016
00:52:32,760 --> 00:52:33,599
come back.

1017
00:53:14,760 --> 00:53:16,599
Your Excellency,

1018
00:53:17,079 --> 00:53:18,960
they said they were
on duty yesterday as well.

1019
00:53:19,239 --> 00:53:20,360
They saw Si Lili

1020
00:53:20,519 --> 00:53:21,599
fleeing out of town.

1021
00:53:21,800 --> 00:53:22,519
Which direction did she go?

1022
00:53:22,639 --> 00:53:23,199
To the north.

1023
00:53:23,840 --> 00:53:25,280
Then a few horses showed up.

1024
00:53:25,519 --> 00:53:27,039
The riders wear bamboo hats
with similar dresses.

1025
00:53:27,079 --> 00:53:28,599
It's difficult to tell
which one is Si Lili.

1026
00:53:28,760 --> 00:53:30,599
Then they went
in their own separate ways.

1027
00:53:33,599 --> 00:53:34,960
So well-prepared they are!

1028
00:53:37,119 --> 00:53:37,880
What's wrong, Your Excellency?

1029
00:53:40,760 --> 00:53:41,440
Nothing.

1030
00:53:42,000 --> 00:53:43,239
I feel like something is not right.

1031
00:53:45,440 --> 00:53:46,159
What is it?

1032
00:53:47,239 --> 00:53:48,079
It's hard to describe it clearly.

1033
00:53:48,760 --> 00:53:49,800
It could be the way

1034
00:53:49,800 --> 00:53:50,960
Si Lili escaped.

1035
00:53:53,440 --> 00:53:56,760
Multiple teams starting out together
to create confusion.

1036
00:53:56,880 --> 00:53:58,599
That's a smart way to escape.

1037
00:53:59,039 --> 00:53:59,679
I know,

1038
00:54:00,079 --> 00:54:01,559
but still something is missed out.

1039
00:54:02,239 --> 00:54:03,039
Let's leave it!

1040
00:54:03,960 --> 00:54:04,760
How do you plan to hunt?

1041
00:54:04,960 --> 00:54:07,199
Your Excellency, please follow me.

1042
00:54:19,639 --> 00:54:20,239
What are you doing?

1043
00:54:21,679 --> 00:54:22,199
Shoot a bird!

1044
00:54:25,239 --> 00:54:25,960
Where is the bird?!

1045
00:54:28,159 --> 00:54:28,840
It will come

1046
00:54:29,239 --> 00:54:29,960
in a minute.

1047
00:54:38,480 --> 00:54:38,920
There it comes!

1048
00:54:51,239 --> 00:54:52,039
A carrier pigeon?!

1049
00:54:53,920 --> 00:54:56,079
A carrier pigeon
of the Investigator's Office.

1050
00:54:58,840 --> 00:55:01,320
Si Lili burnt the boat

1051
00:55:02,280 --> 00:55:03,079
and rode a horse out of town.

1052
00:55:03,760 --> 00:55:04,840
It must attract the attention

1053
00:55:04,840 --> 00:55:06,159
of the Investigator's Office.

1054
00:55:07,239 --> 00:55:09,079
Even though she arranged six teams,

1055
00:55:09,760 --> 00:55:11,320
her rough direction is to the north.

1056
00:55:12,119 --> 00:55:12,880
Most of the pigeons

1057
00:55:14,360 --> 00:55:15,320
from the north towns

1058
00:55:15,400 --> 00:55:16,599
will go through this place.

1059
00:55:21,519 --> 00:55:22,960
Si Lili is already being tracked.

1060
00:55:23,719 --> 00:55:25,280
Multiple teams are hunting her down.

1061
00:55:28,880 --> 00:55:30,360
Wait a minute! How do you know

1062
00:55:30,679 --> 00:55:31,320
the pigeons of the Investigator's Office

1063
00:55:31,320 --> 00:55:32,239
must go through here?

1064
00:55:35,719 --> 00:55:36,719
Honestly,

1065
00:55:37,199 --> 00:55:38,119
I have spent some time in the office

1066
00:55:39,639 --> 00:55:40,960
raising pigeons.

1067
00:55:41,280 --> 00:55:42,119
Won't it be noticed

1068
00:55:42,119 --> 00:55:42,920
that you shot their pigeon?

1069
00:55:43,920 --> 00:55:45,760
The Investigator's Office usually

1070
00:55:45,760 --> 00:55:47,280
sends out several pigeons in one go.

1071
00:55:47,440 --> 00:55:49,440
It's doesn't matter
to have one of them missing.

1072
00:55:49,800 --> 00:55:50,519
Won't anyone notice it?

1073
00:55:51,559 --> 00:55:53,440
As pigeons usually come across
predators like eagles

1074
00:55:54,079 --> 00:55:56,320
during their fly,

1075
00:55:57,079 --> 00:55:58,880
there is natural loss every month.

1076
00:55:59,760 --> 00:56:00,480
Besides,

1077
00:56:00,920 --> 00:56:02,440
I've raised pigeons for some time.

1078
00:56:02,519 --> 00:56:03,199
So I know

1079
00:56:03,320 --> 00:56:04,639
the number of pigeons coming back

1080
00:56:04,840 --> 00:56:05,800
always fluctuates.

1081
00:56:05,920 --> 00:56:07,199
No one will suspect.

1082
00:56:09,320 --> 00:56:11,519
What else have you raised
other than pigeons?

1083
00:56:12,920 --> 00:56:14,599
Why do you ask so?

1084
00:56:14,920 --> 00:56:16,119
Save for a rainy day.

1085
00:56:16,320 --> 00:56:17,719
I must get prepared anyhow.

1086
00:56:34,920 --> 00:56:36,119
Here you go, sir! Tea for you!

1087
00:56:51,119 --> 00:56:51,480
Your Excellency,

1088
00:56:51,719 --> 00:56:52,559
I collected messages
from different towns.

1089
00:56:52,880 --> 00:56:53,679
Two of the teams have been captured.

1090
00:56:53,840 --> 00:56:54,679
Neither of them is Si Lili.

1091
00:56:54,800 --> 00:56:55,960
The rest four teams
are still being hunted.

1092
00:56:59,159 --> 00:57:00,400
How about Fan Xian?
Is he still after her?

1093
00:57:00,800 --> 00:57:01,960
Fan Xian should not
be able to catch up now.

1094
00:57:05,639 --> 00:57:07,800
Does Si Lili keep running
towards the north?

1095
00:57:08,119 --> 00:57:09,280
Yeah, all the way north.

1096
00:57:09,599 --> 00:57:10,519
She should be heading to Beiqi.

1097
00:57:11,440 --> 00:57:12,079
Fetch the map!

1098
00:57:12,639 --> 00:57:13,079
Yes!

1099
00:57:13,440 --> 00:57:15,840
It's always passive
to go from the behind.

1100
00:57:16,440 --> 00:57:17,480
As soon as we can figure out

1101
00:57:17,599 --> 00:57:18,800
where Si Lili

1102
00:57:18,800 --> 00:57:19,559
is running to,

1103
00:57:19,760 --> 00:57:20,840
we will be able to find the path

1104
00:57:20,920 --> 00:57:22,079
she has to go through.

1105
00:57:26,760 --> 00:57:27,679
Your Excellency, check this out!

1106
00:57:27,840 --> 00:57:30,159
This is a territory map I drew of

1107
00:57:31,920 --> 00:57:33,960
the mountains and rivers in the world.

1108
00:57:39,719 --> 00:57:42,239
It's super clear, isn't it?

1109
00:57:44,039 --> 00:57:44,880
I don't understand it at all.

1110
00:57:47,519 --> 00:57:49,039
Your Excellency, first of all,

1111
00:57:49,039 --> 00:57:49,880
we need to confirm

1112
00:57:50,199 --> 00:57:51,679
if Si Lili

1113
00:57:51,760 --> 00:57:52,639
is from Beiqi.

1114
00:57:53,199 --> 00:57:54,360
Her token as a secret agent
is confirmed.

1115
00:57:54,599 --> 00:57:55,280
She is from Beiqi.

1116
00:57:55,559 --> 00:57:56,079
OK.

1117
00:57:56,079 --> 00:57:57,719
So she must go north.

1118
00:57:57,880 --> 00:57:58,760
